WEBVTT

00:03.572 --> 00:05.513
He has highly advanced cognitive skills,...

00:08.957 --> 00:10.159
...the obsessive personality.

00:13.563 --> 00:14.853
Can our son lead a normal life?

00:18.211 --> 00:18.932
Define normal.

00:21.987 --> 00:24.001
Maybe he is capable of much more than we know.

00:32.735 --> 00:34.563
Say you're the head of the Sinaloa cartel.

00:35.507 --> 00:37.161
Who can you trust to track your stolen cash?

00:37.671 --> 00:43.027
He is capable of coming in cold, uncooking years of books and getting out alive.

00:44.397 --> 00:46.036
Imagine the secrets this guy has.

00:46.392 --> 00:46.989
Who are you?

01:00.313 --> 01:01.877
Can our son lead a normal life?

01:02.924 --> 01:03.855
Define normal.

